---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<section id="contacto" class="py-40 bg-[#050505]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 max-w-screen-2xl grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-lg">contactame</span>
            <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold">contacto</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
               Estoy buscando mi próxima gran oportunidad para crecer como desarrollador. Si buscas un perfil proactivo y adaptable segun la demanda, hablemos.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xl text-gray-400 pt-4">
                <Icon name="tabler:map-pin" class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-500" />
                <span>España, Barcelona</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-8">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 font-medium">Descarga mi CV:</p>
                <a href="/cv.pdf" download="Nil_Arroyo_CV.pdf" class="inline-block group relative transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
                    <img 
                        src="/cv-screenshot.jpg" 
                        alt="Descargar CV" 
                        class="w-48 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border-2 border-gray-800 group-hover:border-sky-500 transition-colors"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-xl">
                        <Icon name="tabler:download" class="w-12 h-12 text-white" />
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xgolwbzp" 
            method="POST"
            class="space-y-6 bg-[#0f1115] p-10 md:p-14 rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-800 shadow-2xl">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2">Nombre</label>
                <input required type="text" name="name" class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-5 rounded-2xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-lg transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2">Email</label>
                <input required type="email" name="email" class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-5 rounded-2xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-lg transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2">Mensaje</label>
                <textarea required rows="5" name="message" class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-5 rounded-2xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-lg transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-white text-black py-5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition font-bold text-xl mt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                Enviar Mensaje <Icon name="tabler:send" />
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-gray-600 text-lg mt-32 border-t border-gray-900 pt-12">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nil Arroyo. Built with Astro & Tailwind.</p>
    </div>
</section>